column5: We've been working on this all week, I hope there is still some ice next week. Any OFC'ers interested come on out.
Hey farmer,,,i'll be there as long as i remember,,lol,,,memory these days isn't so good,,so a little reminder wouldn't hurt as time approches!!
*Ok* Farmer i will be there if you buy the (Beer) nice reminder i forget very easy  ?????
Did i just hear,,,,free beer  fishfarmers buy'n????
Looks like I got to get into the piggy bank. I was hoping Spiel was buying  .
I'll be there. I thought Spiel said the beer was on him....?  G
It probably will be by late in the evening, best I bring a change of clothing.
LOL.... Meet you at your place tomorrow evening.  G
I'm leaving my money at home. Spiel buying  .
I will have Bill Parker in tow  G

The tab's on Spiel? I always said you were a great guy!  As much as I would like to go I might not be able to go. I have an important meeting tomorrow morning that I have to be bright eyed and bushy tailed for.
Pikehunter will you be there?  G
Just edited the above Gerritt. If I do get there I will be leaving rather early, how late would it run?
They can run late... but would still be worth your while to drop by for an hour or two..   G
Have a good time out there tonight guys. We're expecting a pictorial essay. HINT: Pics should probably be taken early in the evening.

Gerritt, It would be nice to meet everyone, and the entertainment sounds great too!  Be a shame to miss it, however my meeting is actually a job interview. Actually it sounds like a gang fight as there is 3 of them against me, one of those panel type interviews and one of the interviewers is coming from out of town to see me! Wow, put the pressure on or what?   So if I decide to stay home and study up on my presentation I hope that FF, Spiel and you understand why.  H.

Well I had a blast, Had a few pops, blew some $$ on prize tickets etc... and listened to Italo tell me how good Rapala Taildancers are  I drug Bill Parker along with me who seemed to enjoy himself as well... shot the carp with Spiel for a good portion of the night, and I won a Rod and Reel! (unknowingly until this morning LOL)  and it appears I was sitting beside Sonny all night... did not have a clue it was you sorry bud.  Anyways all in all it was a blast and I am already looking forward to the upcoming meetings.  G
No Gerritt I dunno who you're talking about cause ya sure didn't Drug me... Enjoyed being there guys, nice meeting ya FF's and Mr. Spiel...
Nice to meet you last night *Gerritt* i dont know about this guy called *Spiel* pain in the neck (Right) boys
